ğŸ‘‰Problem 1ï¸âƒ£: Population Census

Given the CITY and COUNTRY tables, query the sum of the populations of all cities where the CONTINENT is â€˜Asiaâ€™.
Note: CITY.CountryCode and COUNTRY.Code are matching key columns. 

ğŸ‘‰SOLUTION:MYSQL
----------------
SELECT 
    SUM(c.POPULATION) AS total_population
FROM 
    CITY c
JOIN 
    COUNTRY co
ON 
    c.COUNTRYCODE = co.CODE
WHERE 
    co.CONTINENT = 'Asia';



